717222f-a.text:
Broadway, north from Reade Street, showing prominently, the 16-story Central Syndicate Building, at the N.E. corner of Pearl Street, and beyond that (building with clock tower) the New York Life Insurance Company Building, from Catherine Lane to Leonard Street.
April 18, 1937
P. L. Sperr
